Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This corporate office and lab facility is located in the heart of Rowville with immediate access to Eastlink and the Monash Freeway via Wellington Road.

The property features:

• Fully furnished top floor corporate accommodation with 18 offices, 32 open plan work stations and multiple meeting rooms
• Large (100 people) training area and kitchen
• 25 car spaces
• Plus access to multiple laboratories can be made available upon request

* 700sqm approx
* Full concrete panel, up to 9m clearance approx
* Ability to customize your office/showroom requirements
* Industrial 1 zoning
* Sought after location - close proximity to Eastlink via Wellington Road & Ferntree Gully Road

- Long term lease to the highest calibre global tenant (listed on the Paris Stock Exchange)

- Flexible offering over two titles

- Premium grade office accommodation

- Whilst purpose built for the current tenant, the properties provide flexible and functional accommodation

- High clearance to the warehouse areas of approximately 8.5 and 10 metres respectively

- Combined passing income of approximately $720,141 per annum net

- Situated approximately 25 kilometres east of the Melbourne CBD in a tightly held industrial precinct

- Excellent access to the surrounding road network.

High quality investment opportunity subject to a long term lease to the Process Group (Subsidiary of Suez Environnement).

For sale via EOI closing Tuesday 9 December at 3.00pm AEST

*Approximately
